<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹高兴得无法入睡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天是上学的第一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想着自己将要学习的各种东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳升起时，他跳下床，拿着他的新书，向学校跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，爸爸！”他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹边走边开心地自言自语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天，我会学习阅读。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天，我会学习写作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后天，我会学习数学。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会变得很聪明！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会变得足够聪明，可以找到工作赚钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会给爸爸买一件新的外套，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一件绿色丝绸搭配钻石扣子的好看的外套。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为了我的课本卖掉了他的外套。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他听到了远处传来的音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向着音乐传来的地方走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到了很多人，还有一个颜色鲜艳的帐篷和一个大型标志。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！我真希望今天不用去上学！这里真有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他已经忘记了杰佩托外套的事儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思打搅一下。”匹诺曹向村民问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “那个标志是什么意思？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么问我？你不认识字吗？”村民笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不认识字。”匹诺曹不好意思地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里写着‘木偶剧院，四里拉’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>演出在五分钟后开始。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是你不认识字。你现在应该在学校。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想去上学！”匹诺曹叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以借四里拉吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹不好意思去乞讨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他真的很想去看演出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有四里拉。”村民说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我不会借给你，你需要卖给我一些东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我除了衣服和这本书，什么都没有！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你就卖给我你的书吧。”村民说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道这本书的价格高于四个里拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹接过钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹跑到帐篷里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>笛子和鼓在演奏一首新歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些木偶被带出来跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，他们和我一样是用木头做成的！”匹诺曹兴奋地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑近舞台想看得更清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是他们不是真的！他们需要被绳子带着跳舞！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以比他们跳得好，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也不需要别人用绳子来控制我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹跳上木偶舞台大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是神奇的匹诺曹。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳着舞，旋转着，跳着，翻转着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观众们大笑着，欢呼着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “真棒，匹诺曹！你是有史以来最棒的木偶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，音乐停了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人从幕后走向台前，抓住了匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“演出结束了，乡亲们！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你们想看神奇的匹诺曹，必须另外付钱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把匹诺曹拽到了后台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命，救命！”匹诺曹叫道，“救救我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹很害怕这个男人生气的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从现在开始你是我的了。你要为我赚很多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个不用线来控制的木偶！哈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人开始想象一堆又一堆的钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拜托了，先生。我是杰佩托的儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我需要去上学。请放我走吧。”匹诺曹央求道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是别人的儿子？是一个学生？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈！这真是一个天大的笑话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们马上离开，这样杰佩托就无法找到你了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人把匹诺曹关在一个笼子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把笼子藏在马车上的毯子下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在没有人能找到你了。”男人笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他收拾好他的帐篷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，对不起。”匹诺曹哭着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快救救我！我想爸爸。呜呜呜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>